{"tid":1554942,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"若蓮喪子","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T11:26:02.000Z","uid":143093,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"391de0665b81018e763a993947b2418d1b57cd1a","tid":1554942,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"丁酉年秋，酷吏若蓮長子自盡，民不以為悲，反竊喜。吏斥曰禽獸，民怒詰之：「昔吏行峻法，先生棄世，學子尋短，死者甚眾，何不以悲！何不思過而自省？反諷黃泉之下諸先生學子！十數載前，先有羅門范氏嘲先生之亡，曰：「若為苛政故，亡者豈只一二乎？」；及至學子歿者逾七十眾，猶有九日連殞七命者。吏吳克儉又譏其事，曰：「生徒尋死蓋因未嘗遠謀，於未未規之，故取死之道矣。」二吏身居朝堂，掌司徒事，見師生死，冷嘲熱諷，何鮮仁也！今若蓮喪子，吏偽憐之，更未憐昔眾師生。民仇吏而悅，喜見其悲，不亦人性乎？非子曰：『以直報怨，以德報德』乎？先有不仁之官，後有無情之民。百姓受苦，師生洩恨。喜見官悲，樂其兒亡。揮筆成輻，賀其早喪！今日之事，豈非無因？所謂因果，當如此狀。師生自戕，酷吏未助，反笑諸子，自問其過。今日吏悲，斥我無情。早知今日，何必當初！！」"},{"pid":"b855fd6af9c54000598fb774dd257381a0c91166","tid":1554942,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874082454d449c9669422974120af3b52415aeba","tid":1554942,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b855fd6af9c54000598fb774dd257381a0c91166","tid":1554942,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:26:25.000Z","msg":"失望！無人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fa085e0115dd396772e078b417d769ee8cfbdf","tid":1554942,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874082454d449c9669422974120af3b52415aeba","tid":1554942,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b855fd6af9c54000598fb774dd257381a0c91166","tid":1554942,"uid":152123,